Mike to choose, too,

17:10.772 --> 17:13.692
there'll be such heartache.

17:13.776 --> 17:15.861
So few opportunities for you.

17:15.944 --> 17:17.496
I know. I've heard the jokes.

17:17.579 --> 17:18.646
I better hope they do

17:18.698 --> 17:19.830
<i>a musical of The Joy Luck Club</i>

17:19.915 --> 17:20.866
<i>or Memoirs of a Geisha.</i>

17:20.950 --> 17:22.501
I don't care.

17:22.585 --> 17:24.118
